            . On the afternoon of the 8th of September, I put sixteen loaves of bread on the board, and sent the prisoner to the same place; he only delivered twelve - he came back intoxicated; I paid him and discharged him in about two hours; here are only twelve entered in Mr. Selwin's book, and I am sure I gave him sixteen: I am sure he took sixteen, and took them all at once - he was not to go to any other customer, and brought none back.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. My master put down sixteen - I delivered them on the shelves; I did not count the bread.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290910-264-person2422">
